00:25:35.320 --> 00:25:38.210
So [INAUDIBLE] science
with new techniques,

00:25:38.210 --> 00:25:41.100
and Laura was saying
that with new telescopes,

00:25:41.100 --> 00:25:44.640
we could [? get ?] more detail
