00:55:53.460 --> 00:55:54.510
I'm not sure.

00:55:54.510 --> 00:55:55.940
However, that life
is still going

00:55:55.940 --> 00:55:59.894
to be around when somebody
else comes looking for us,

00:55:59.894 --> 00:56:00.560
I'm pretty sure.

00:56:00.560 --> 00:56:03.680
It takes a lot to kill life
