00:56:26.370 --> 00:56:27.330
day in and day out?

00:56:32.600 --> 00:56:37.790
- So I teach a class of
250 undergrad students.

00:56:37.790 --> 00:56:40.040
They're just coming into
Cornell and love my class.

00:56:40.040 --> 00:56:41.480
And so sometimes they also--

00:56:41.480 --> 00:56:43.440
so the existential
crisis will stay.

00:56:43.440 --> 00:56:45.496
It's just going to
become different.

00:56:45.496 --> 00:56:47.760
This connection
[? is to the ?] stars.

